<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>予約管理ログイン | TEAL MUSIC</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <style>
      main {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 24px auto;
        padding: 0 16px;
      }
      .page-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .login-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        padding: 16px 16px 20px;
      }
      .field {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .field label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .field input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 8px 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .error {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #fee2e2;
        color: #b91c1c;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      .btn-row {
        margin-top: 8px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        padding: 8px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: none;
        background: #0ea5e9;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 14px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .note {
        margin-top: 12px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main>
      <h1 class="page-title">既存生徒予約管理ログイン</h1>

      <div class="login-card">
        <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/reserve/admin-login" method="POST">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="adminId">ID</label>
            <input type="text" id="adminId" name="adminId" required />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="password">パスワード</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required />
          </div>

          <div class="btn-row">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">ログイン</button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <p class="note">
          ※ この画面はTEAL MUSICスタッフ専用です。<br />
          一般のお客様は体験レッスンお申し込みフォームからご予約ください。
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
